            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="22975666">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">全国性报纸市场倾向于催生出在政治上更加分化的报界。


为什么?</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22975666/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-12-06 11:17</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                全国性报纸市场倾向于催生出在政治上更加分化的报界。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>为什么?
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
